OL,7,FWords by Senior Producer Jack Abbey
OL,9,FOne of the UK's fastest-growing online
OL,10,Fgambling companies is being accused of
OL,11,Fbreaching rules designed to protect
OL,12,Fchildren in its online advertising and
OL,13,Fmarketing, ITV News has learned.
OL,15,FSocial media posts made by Midnite are
OL,16,Fthe subject of a complaint made
OL,17,Fagainst the company to the Advertising
OL,18,FStandards Authority (ASA).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
