OL,7,FAmong the content in the complaint
OL,8,Fmade by academics are X posts
OL,9,Fincluding pictures and jokes about
OL,10,Fhigh-profile footballers such as Harry
OL,11,FKane, Harry Maguire and Jack Grealish.
OL,13,FAll of those figures are identified in
OL,14,Fthe CAP code as being likely to be of
OL,15,Fstrong appeal to children and
OL,16,Feffectively banned from appearing in
OL,17,Fgambling advertising.
