OL,7,FThe nature of content marketing means
OL,8,Fthat none of the figures pictured in
OL,9,Fthe posts are involved with or paid by
OL,10,FMidnite.
OL,12,FResearch done by the Bristol team has
OL,13,Fshown that content marketing is four
OL,14,Ftimes more appealing to children than
OL,15,Fit is to adults.
OL,17,FIn total, the posts have been viewed
OL,18,Fmore than 4.5 million times on
OL,19,FMidnite's social media channels.
