OL,7,FOne post on X of Harry Maguire's face
OL,8,Fimposed onto a Brazilian football
OL,9,Fplayer has been viewed more than 2.6
OL,10,Fmillion times.
OL,12,FThe company has 70,000 followers on X
OL,13,Fand nearly 50,000 on Instagram.
OL,15,F"These forms of content marketing
OL,16,Fobscure the promotional nature of the
OL,17,Fmessage and blur the lines between
OL,18,Fentertainment and advertising for a
OL,19,Fhigh-risk product," Dr Raffaello
OL,20,FRossi, one of the lead researchers,
OL,21,Fsaid.
