OL,7,F"These posts appear as entertaining
OL,8,Fcontent, making them harder to
OL,9,Frecognise as gambling promotions and
OL,10,Fmore likely to be shared widely
OL,11,Fonline, especially by children."
OL,13,FFigures from the Gambling Commission
OL,14,Fpublished last year show that the
OL,15,Fnumber of children experiencing
OL,16,Fproblems with gambling soared to
OL,17,F85,000, more than double the 2023
OL,18,Ffigure.
