OL,7,FMidnite is not a high street gambling
OL,8,Fbrand, but it is popular online and
OL,9,Fgrowing fast.
OL,11,FStarted in 2015 in London, it
OL,12,Fdescribes itself as an 'e-betting
OL,13,Fplatform' that allows users to place
OL,14,Fbets on a wide range of subjects, from
OL,15,Fsports to politics and video games.
