OL,7,FIShowSpeed in particular has tens of
OL,8,Fmillions of social media followers,
OL,9,Fand the researchers in their complaint
OL,10,Fsaid: "He is widely recognised as a
OL,11,Fyouth influencer and role model, and
OL,12,Fhis inclusion in gambling ads is not
OL,13,Fonly inappropriate under the CAP Code
OL,14,Fbut deeply concerning given his strong
OL,15,Fresonance with under-18s".
OL,17,FThis is not the first time Midnite's
OL,18,Fsocial media posts have been shown to
OL,19,Fthe ASA.
