OL,8,Fresearchers list four previous
OL,9,Foccasions they raised the issue of
OL,10,FMidnite and its content marketing,
OL,11,Fwith the first being over a year ago.
OL,13,FITV News has reached out to Midnite
OL,14,Ffor comment but has received no
OL,15,Fresponse.
