OL,7,FThe ASA said: "We're aware of the
OL,8,Fcomplainant's concerns about 'content
OL,9,Fmarketing' and we've been engaging
OL,10,Fwith them and other stakeholders on
OL,11,Fthe issue in recent months. This is a
OL,12,Frelatively new form of marketing that
OL,13,Fraises complex questions around
OL,14,Fjurisdiction and the boundaries
OL,15,Fbetween advertising and editorial
OL,16,Fcontent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
