OL,7,F"We have investigations underway that
OL,8,Fwill bring clarity to these boundary
OL,9,Fissues. In the meantime, we can
OL,10,Fconfirm that this week, we received a
OL,11,Fcomplaint about social media posts by
OL,12,FMidnite, and we are currently
OL,13,Fassessing it to establish what
OL,14,Fadditional action to take."
OL,16,FITV News has also contacted Snooker
OL,17,FHalo World Championship and
OL,18,FSouthampton FC for comment.
